          </div>
          <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.35rem;color:#1A1A1A;line-height:1.15;margin-bottom:.75rem">Commercial Roofing Systems Explained: TPO, EPDM, Metal &amp; More</h2>
          <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:1.25rem">A guide to commercial roofing options for Tampa Bay business owners — pros, cons, and costs of each system.</p>
        </div>
      </a>

      </div>

      <p id="no-posts-msg" class="text-center py-16" style="display:none;color:#888;font-size:1.1rem;line-height:1.7">
        New articles are on the way — check back soon!
      </p>
